ESPN Ratings

espn_ratings.Rd

ESPN Ratings

Get FPI historical rating data (most recent of each year) Adapted from sabinanalytic's fork of the cfbfastR repo

espn_ratings_fpi(year = 2019)

Arguments

year

Year

Source

https://github.com/sabinanalytics/cfbfastR/blob/master/R/cfbd_ratings_fpi.R

Value

A data frame with 20 variables:

year

double.

id

character.

name

character.

abbr

character.

row_n

integer.

fpi

character.

fpi_rk

character.

trend

character.

proj_w

character.

proj_l

character.

win_out

double.

win_6

double.

win_div

double.

playoff

double.

nc_game

double.

nc_win

double.

win_conf

double.

w

character.

l

character.

t

character.
